{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/how-to-hide-out-of-stock-products","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1794,"date":"2022-10-24T10:35:18","date_gmt":"2022-10-24T10:35:18","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1794"},"modified":"2022-12-17T21:09:07","modified_gmt":"2022-12-17T21:09:07","slug":"how-to-hide-out-of-stock-products","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/how-to-hide-out-of-stock-products/","title":{"rendered":"How to hide out of stock products [Free themes]"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>When you have an e-commerce store on Shopify it&#8217;s normal to handle a wide variety of products, some of which sell more than others. That means sooner or later they&#8217;ll run out of stock before you get a chance to replenish them with your supplier, and in the meanwhile you might not want them visible to your clients at all.<br><br>How to accomplish that might not be too obvious at first glance and some solutions can also cause other unintended bugs, such as leaving empty spaces in your collection page. This is no longer something you&#8217;ll have to worry about however, as this tutorial will teach you how to easily hide any products that go out of stock.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"NoticeBox NoticeBox--info\"><p>This tutorial is compatible with all Shopify&#8217;s official free themes: Dawn, Refresh, Colorblock, Taste, Ride, Studio, Crave, Sense &amp; Craft.</p></div>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-theme\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-hiding-unavailable-products\">Hiding unavailable products</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, go to <strong>Online Store &gt; Themes &gt; Actions &gt; Edict Code &gt; Snippets &gt; Add a new snippet</strong></li><li>In the new box that appears type in: <br><br><strong>ezfy-hide-sold-out</strong><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1408\" height=\"849\" class=\"wp-image-1800\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/14p8ilcc.bmp\" alt=\"Typing the name &quot;ezfy-hide-sold-out&quot; for the new snippet file\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/14p8ilcc.bmp 1408w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/14p8ilcc-850x513.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/14p8ilcc-1200x724.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/14p8ilcc-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px\" /><br></li><li>Inside the new file paste the following code:<br><br>[gist]5992aacc7687d656393ec06a61158bc5[gist]<br></li><li>Save your changes and you&#8217;re done!<br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1501\" height=\"794\" class=\"wp-image-1802\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/g6qc2g1f.bmp\" alt=\"Saving changes to the code\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/g6qc2g1f.bmp 1501w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/g6qc2g1f-850x450.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/g6qc2g1f-1200x635.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/g6qc2g1f-768x406.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1501px) 100vw, 1501px\" /><br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-final-step-adding-the-code-to-the-website\">Final step: adding the code to the website </h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Find the file named exactly <strong>theme.liquid</strong>.</li><li>Inside this file, press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and search for:<br><br><strong>&lt;body</strong></li><li>Paste the following code <strong>after </strong>the <strong>&lt;body</strong> tag you found and save:<br><br><code>{% include 'ezfy-hide-sold-out' %}</code><br><br><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"736\" height=\"515\" class=\"wp-image-2031\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot_1.png\" alt=\"Inserting the ezfy-hide-sold-out snippet to the theme.liquid body\"><br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-conclusion\">Conclusion</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If your followed this guide through, any product that runs out of stock will be automatically hidden from the collection page, and once it&#8217;s available again it&#8217;ll reappear for your clients without you having to do anything.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/add-slideshow-shopify-no-apps\">&#8211; How to make slideshow images stop cutting off</a><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/UKO9ViFXaWQ\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\">&amp;lt;br>&amp;lt;a href=&#8221;https://ezfycode.com/blog/collection-with-tabs-shopify-section-tutorial&#8221; target=&#8221;_blank&#8221; rel=&#8221;noreferrer noopener&#8221;>- Add a collection tabs slider to any store (copy/paste, no apps, blazing fast)&amp;lt;/a>&amp;lt;iframe width=&#8221;560&#8243; height=&#8221;315&#8243; src=&#8221;https://www.youtube.com/embed/MuD0FgqENoc&#8221; title=&#8221;YouTube video player&#8221; frameborder=&#8221;0&#8243; allow=&#8221;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&#8221; allowfullscreen=&#8221;&#8221;>&amp;amp;amp;lt;br>&amp;amp;amp;lt;a href=&#8221;https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps&#8221;>- Disable right click, image and text copying and improve your store&#8217;s security&amp;amp;amp;lt;/a></iframe><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/collection-with-tabs-shopify-section-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; How to add a collection with tabs section to any theme (copy/paste, no apps, blazing fast)</a><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/MuD0FgqENoc\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\"><br><br></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Automatically hide out of stock products without leaving empty spaces in your collection page.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":1808,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[655,626,657,435,663,649,652,646,660],"image_alt":"","featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/remove-2-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/remove-2-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/remove-2-1200x675.png","categories_names":["Blog"],"acf":[],"tag_names":["Colorblock Theme","Craft Theme","Crave Theme","Dawn Theme","Refresh theme","Ride theme","Sense Theme","Studio Theme","Taste theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/remove-2.png","featured_image_url_alt":"How to hide out of stock products","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1794"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.e